item.content:
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-12 col-md-12 text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data/uploads/medical-tourism-logo.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;
		&lt;h4&gt;Department of Medical Tourism&lt;/h4&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gateway Clinics &amp;amp; Hospitals&lt;/strong&gt; provide personalized and culturally appropriate care for International patients. We are proud to present the comprehensive Gastro and Gynaec packages designed to meet the needs of International patients. We have team of Consultants for expert opinions, diagnostics, procedures and surgeries and treatment or long term illnesses / diseases and rehabilitation / recovery. Our International Services Desk ensures that our international customers receive excellent treatment and get all the possible support during their stay in our hospital. We want all our patients to feel safe, comfortable and taken good care of and - as much as possible - feel at home at Gateway Clinics &amp;amp; Hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-8 col-md-8&quot;&gt;
		&lt;h5&gt;Services :&lt;/h5&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Airport pick-up and drop&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Accommodation for the companion&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Room Service&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Interpretation services&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Coordinator with 24 hour availability&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Help desk&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Currency exchange&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Local site seeing arrangement Process&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4&quot;&gt;(% gallery name=medical-tourism %)&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-12 col-md-12 text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;All you have to do is get in touch with the Gateway Hospital International Patient Care Team. You can email us your query along with your medical reports to&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:gatewayclinicscoimbatore@gmail.com&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;gatewayclinicscoimbatore@gmail.com&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;We will respond to your query within 3 days. We will share the treatment plan, estimated days of stay in India and a quote for your treatment. If the concerned doctor feels that he/she needs to know more or view any recent reports, we will communicate to you regarding the same accordingly.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Once you have decided to travel to India, make sure that you have the following documents:&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-12 col-md-12&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Your Passport&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;A Medical Visa&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Photo Identifications&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Carry all your previous medical records. Include all the diagnostic test reports and surgery reports, treatment records and laboratory results.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;All films / CDs (for example, X-rays, MRIs, CT scans,) along with their relevant reports.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;space&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/fav-icon.png&quot; /&gt;Prescriptions for any medications that you must take regularly and bring them with you.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-12 col-md-12 text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Keep us Informed on your Arrival Schedule in advance. This will help us in making necessary arrangements such as your transport, appointments, room reservations, etc. The International Patient Care Center will make arrangements for receiving you at the Airport. You will be provided with a one point contact or Coordinator at our hospital and personalised care at every step of your stay with us.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;When your treating expert takes a decision of discharging you from the hospital, we will hand over all copies of your medical reports. Once you are back in your country of residence, your follow up care can be made via email/phone/web or video conferencing.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
